Name: The Guild Garage
Title: 'Vette Vibes
Desc: Tommy, Talon and Greg get a '53 Corvette running again after years in storage.
LongDescription: Tommy, Talon and Greg get a '53 Corvette running again after years in storage; it's a flame-engulfed fire-up for Talon and Ron and the '85 Camaro; Dave checks an item off his bucket list when he and Janice test drive the new C8 Corvette.
